> Required Notice: Copyright 2024 / Authors: Oren Wei (weioren), Jeffrey Khong (jeffreykhong1), Lily Zhu (lilyzhu31) / Organization: Reva / Github: https://github.com/co-leaders/reva

## Changes and New Works License

The licensor grants you an additional copyright license to
make changes and new works based on the software for any
